<div class="pt2 mt0 mb0 mt3--md mb0--md" style="background-color: #f8f8f8; margin: auto;">
    <div class="paragraph-centered">
        <h2 class="fw--600 sans--medium mb2 color--beam-blue pr1 pl1 tc">The Vision</h2>
        <h2 class="fw--400 sans--body-new mb3 pl1 pr1 tc paragraph">We’re here to push the boundaries of what’s possible in the wellness space, and we can’t do it without you. Beam products are premium, science-backed, and lab-tested - and they work. Our vision for the future: help bring humanity to the next stage of our wellness evolution. Come along for the ride. </h2>
